ss formula from [arXiv:1804.07744] to the von Neumann algebra setting by\nshowing that the spectral mass of the bands is topologically rigid under\ndeformations and we conclude that these masses are quantized in some important\ncases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Apr 2018 17:54:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2018 14:45:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 May 2018 11:36:55 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 15:34:58 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 11 Dec 2018 13:56:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-12"}
